            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605902711834-8b9a2be7606c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" 
            alt="札幌市の住宅地" 
            class="w-full h-32 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-4">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">札幌市の住宅地比較：東区・白石区・豊平区</h3>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
